{"tid":2245260,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人係時候要take side，支持Trump/共和黨","createTime":"2020-10-16T05:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T19:45:27.000Z","uid":35870,"like":28,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d8ddc94823b5d5a31eb744ac0bf408042017d4","tid":2245260,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"呢個世界無中立，我地對住其他人就識講，對住自己就唔識<br />\n而家連中共都take side揀Biden，敖狗直頭拎住香港人嘅身份take side揀Biden，但連登仔仲話要爭取兩黨支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界無中立架，大事大非面前，民主黨同共和黨兩個，你只能撐一個<br />\n<br />\n唔好拎蔣介石出黎講，蔣介石失去杜魯門支持係因為杜魯門on9，係因為美國一大班中國通畀中國洗晒腦，係因為美國同而家一樣有一大班對共產黨存有美好幻想嘅左翼份子。<br />\n<br />\n所以身為香港人，係更加唔應該袖手旁觀。連中共都落場，香港人邊有得置身事外？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b681185c719fa9362b7961853890b43d56c3cb","tid":2245260,"uid":100155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識撚：不介入選舉，唔好激嬲民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好令美國人反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人舉美國旗都會令美國人反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共不斷送錢比民主黨權貴家族旗下嘅公司，不斷動用國家機器左右美國政局，媒體同社會（甚至特登叫條𡃁塔利班公開支持侵侵，想激起美國人對侵嘅怨恨 令侵落選）<br />\n而香港人連retweet都話介入人地選舉唔太好。宜家唔係君子之爭，而係決定你同我將來命運嘅一場選舉<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">任何有良知嘅人 都唔可以喺呢刻沈默</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">拜登克林頓家族等民主黨精英，根本唔係奶共咁簡單，直頭係中共喺美國嘅照應</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國制裁winning 11，賣先進武器比台灣防守，封鎖中國喺南海嘅行動，不斷加強同澳日印度軍事合作，國務卿聲援12港人，訪台，聲援台灣選舉，抵制被中國玩壞嘅跨國組織⋯<br />\n<br />\n美國幫香港人唔係必然<br />\n如果拜登當選，所有呢啲野全部都唔會再發生。拜登團隊見都唔肯見香港抗爭者，雨傘時奧巴馬政府對香港人wfc，對中國各種擴張 偷竊 間諜 滲透活動亦完全wfc，拜登話中國只係競爭者而唔係敵人（喺佢地眼中中共=中國=中國人，敵視中共係racism，亦損害自己利益，唔應該decouple中國）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴晚Twitter不斷封鎖對民主黨嘅不利消息 <br />\n呢樣野宜家醞釀緊 <br />\n<br />\n拜登嗰副虛偽嘅説辭同佢不斷坐大中共嘅惡行，企圖取消對中關稅，默許佢地嘅反人道惡行，隨時將台灣香港當confom出賣，帶美國入翻被極權國家玩壞嘅組織去迎合佢哋嘅規矩，帶領民主國家開啟奶共新時代⋯如果唔想以上發生，就襯宜家幫手retweet發大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1316501350658707456?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1316501350658707456%3Fs%3D21&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=140d416f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1316501350658707456%3Fs%3D21&h=eb86bfa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1316501350658707456?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1316535709021491200?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1316535709021491200%3Fs%3D21&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=3f599413\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1316535709021491200%3Fs%3D21&h=468e52f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1316535709021491200?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1316526465522040832?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1316526465522040832%3Fs%3D21&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=05402522\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1316526465522040832%3Fs%3D21&h=03ac65fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1316526465522040832?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1316471873467822080?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1316471873467822080%3Fs%3D21&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=b17b5d26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1316471873467822080%3Fs%3D21&h=c35bab8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.c